This directory contains the code implemented to calibrate ECal using a movable radioactive source.

Coordinators for this subdir are Francesco Safai Tehrani <francesco.safaitehrani@roma1.infn.it> and Fabio Ferrarotto <fabio.ferrarotto@roma1.infn.it>

Windows directory contains source code from windows S/W developed on Visuals Studio

The PECco (Padme Electromagnetic Calorimeter calibration online) subdir contains the Python code for the client-server system implemented to perform the online calibration of the ECal. 
